        "width": 760,
        "height": 220,
        "color": 4,
        "content": "## \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f Onboarding \u2014 Part 2: GHL Setup\n\nTriggered by Part 1 (DB Enrichment) ONLY when all required fields are validated.\n\nReceives an `onboarding_request_id` \u2192 loads the staged record \u2192 creates GHL sub-account \u2192 applies snapshot \u2192 saves full agent config to Supabase.\n\n**Safety gate:** If GHL creation fails, the workflow stops immediately. No partial state is created."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-ghl",
      "name": "Sticky Note - GHL",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        840,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 500,
        "height": 220,
        "color": 4,
        "content": "## GHL Sub-Account Creation\nCreate new sub-account and apply SMRT snapshot.\n\n**SNAPSHOT_ID** must be set as an n8n variable (`$vars.SNAPSHOT_ID`) or hardcoded here.\n\nGHL Created? gate stops the flow if creation fails."
      }
    },
